title: Live In Beautiful Hiouchi And Be Your Own Boss! 2040, 2080
text:
Live In Beautiful Hiouchi And Be Your Own Boss! 2040, 2080 ad date: 09/30/2015 
And Be Your Own Boss! 2040, 2080 Hwy 199, Crescent City, CA Situated adjacent to Jedediah Smith Redwood State Park and the Smith River is the Hiouchi RV Resort. Situated on 29.5 beautiful acres with 120 spaces plus tent camping. Resort has full hook ups, laundry facility, hot showers, recreation hall, fish cleaning area, propane gas, and phones. Short walk to state park where you can enjoy hiking, swimming, rafting, kayaking or take a quiet drift boat trip down the river through the ancient redwoods while fishing for world class steelhead and salmon. MLS 1365087 $1,700,000 Kurt Stremberg, Agent 785 E. Washington Blvd #2, Crescent City Cell: 707-954-1732
